OL,3,CUkrainian mother dies in car crash
OL,4,Cafter fleeing war
OL,6,FTributes have been paid to an
OL,7,F"intelligent" and "hard-working"
OL,8,Fmother who died in a crash at the end
OL,9,Fof January, after escaping the war in
OL,10,FUkraine.
OL,12,FTetiana Martynova, 40 from , was in
OL,13,Fthe UK after fleeing Ukraine when in
OL,14,FFebruary 2022.
OL,16,FShe died in a collision on the A4067
OL,17,FNeath Road, in the Morriston area of ,
OL,18,Fon Wednesday January 31.
