OL,6,F"Tania was an impressive woman,
OL,7,Fmultilingual, intelligent, high-
OL,8,Fflying, hard-working, committed and
OL,9,Fdiligent in her tender care of Illia.
OL,11,F"She was driven to scholastic
OL,12,Fachievement here in Swansea, building
OL,13,Fon her Ukrainian excellence in
OL,14,Faccountancy with further
OL,15,Fqualifications and working so hard for
OL,16,Fa local Swansea company utilising her
OL,17,Fimpressive range of skills.
