OL,3,CUkrainian mother dies in car crash
OL,4,Cafter fleeing war
OL,6,F"She was a stalwart of the Ukrainian
OL,7,Fcommunity in Swansea, playing her full
OL,8,Fpart in all their social and cultural
OL,9,Factivities, marking the continued
OL,10,Fdefiance of her nation.
OL,12,F"Her warm and pleasant personality
OL,13,Fpermeated every gathering.
OL,15,F"Lives here in Wales were hugely
OL,16,Fenriched by knowing Tania. Her
OL,17,Fnumerous friends and work colleagues
OL,18,Fare all devastated by her sudden
OL,19,Fpassing.
