OL,3,CUkrainian mother dies in car crash
OL,4,Cafter fleeing war
OL,6,F"We are all grateful to the emergency
OL,7,Fservices at the scene of this terrible
OL,8,Faccident for their diligence and care,
OL,9,Fand also for the supreme
OL,10,Fprofessionalism of the medical and
OL,11,Fnursing care on the critical care unit
OL,12,Fat the University Hospital of Wales in
OL,13,FCardiff.
OL,15,F"Huge thanks to all. We are
OL,16,Fdevastated. Our hearts are broken.
OL,18,F"Tania became like a daughter to us
OL,19,Fboth. Our tears flow for a remarkable
OL,20,Fyoung woman. Ukraine has lost one of
OL,21,Fits finest."
